@@TJvPcx
Description:
This class is a wrapper for the PCX format. if you want to use this format, just include the JvGraphics in your project, and then, you can simply use a TImage component. That's all. It supports loading and saving Monochrome, 16 colors, 256 Colors and 16 Million colors. (1,4,8 and 24 bits)

